Class DiagnosisKeysDirectory

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Directory<WritableOnDisk>, Writable<WritableOnDisk>
    public class DiagnosisKeysDirectory
extends DirectoryOnDisk
    A Directory containing the file and directory structure that mirrors the API defined in the OpenAPI definition /services/distribution/api_v1.json. Available countries (endpoint /version/v1/diagnosis-keys/country) are statically set to only "DE". The dates and respective hours (endpoint /version/v1/diagnosis-keys/country/DE/date) will be created based on the actual DiagnosisKeys given to the constructor.
